Changes that seem small and unimportant at first will compound into remarkable results if you're willing to stick with them for years. I make it a habit to read, first thing in the morning, a few pages from highly recommended business books. I read before turning on any electronic devices. This atomic habit, initiated years ago, has resulted in my library of business knowledge. 

